{
  "stem": "5758.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I took note of him, what he said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I just wanted to satisfy somehow or other my hunger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Surrounding it, I remember, surrounding where we sat there when they approached, a lot of bodies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "A lot of bodies were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I [SIGHS] wanted to talk to an English officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I said to him that I-- I've a brother who I believe is in England and another brother who's in America.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We'll take note of all that here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Next day, we were interviewed, written down everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I don't know if it was the next day or somehow a few days later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "At one time, the army could not provide us with-- with food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So they organized of people who were able to walk to get a wheelbarrow, and said, go into the village.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Go-- go into houses and take from the Germans, and we'll go with you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We will go with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "The-- the English soldiers, two soldiers came with us, and we will take from the Germans food for the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we loaded up big ham and salami and-- and rice and whatever we-- flour and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] A lot of people showing off showed me they were taking money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There were diamonds with-- you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I only was thinking of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And when I went into one of these houses, I saw hidden away, underneath a board, a picture of a-- of Hitler, Adolf Hitler, in a frame, beautiful frame.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "That took my-- tore up this here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And one of the old men-- [SPEAKING GERMAN] 'You dirty Jew.' So I went to him, and I hit that old man until he collapsed.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
